s in terms of their expectations, aspirations, diverse difficulties and the strategies they deploy to deal with these difficulties.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aEducation, HigherzGreat Britain. 0aForeign studyxSocial aspectszGreat Britain. 0aStudents, ForeignzGreat Britain. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Psycholinguistics.2bisacsh  aArab students.  aEFL.  aIntercultural communication.  aInternational students.  aLanguage learning strategies.  aSLA.  aSociocultural perspectives.  afuture self.  afuture visions.  ahigher education.  aidentities.  alanguage acquisition.  alanguage learning goals.  amotivation.  astrategy use.  astudy abroad experiences.  astudy abroad.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2018 Englishz978311060407808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2018z9783110603170oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060678240uhttps://doi.org/10.21832/978178892224140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781788922241423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781788922241/original  a978-3-11-060407-8  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060678-2  MultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHE